p: At 9h after exposure, significant differences were observed between repellency of 0.625%, 1.25%, 2.5%, and 5% concentrations of Oregano essential oil and 33% DEET (P< 0.001), while the differences between 10%, 20%, and 40% oregano essential oil and 33% DEET were not significant (P=0.21) ( Fig. 5).
